title: TEAM AVERAGE 2.0
description:
Team Average the movie, presented by Monster Children and Hurley.

Directed by Riley Blakeway. 

Dylan Rieder, Natas, Greyson Fletcher, Ryan Wilson, Jack Fardell, Alex Gray, and Chippa Wilson tearing New Zealand to bits. Pointless hyping it up. Just watch. It's brilliant.
